# Model weights go through Git LFS.
#
# These previously carried a second pair of rules — `*.safetensors !filter !merge
# !diff` — which UNSET the filter attribute set here, so LFS never actually ran and
# every checkpoint was committed as a raw ~87 MB blob. Four of them are already in
# history and .git is ~483 MB as a result. Removing the unset lines makes LFS engage
# for new commits; excising the existing blobs needs a separate history rewrite.
*.safetensors filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.bin filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
